The movie comes out July 10th and stars Ben
Kingsley as a wealthy man, dying from cancer,

00:03:00.790 --> 00:03:02.550
who undergoes a radical medical procedure
that transfers his consciousness into the

00:03:02.550 --> 00:03:04.600
body of a healthy young man, played by Ryan
Reynolds.

